553
00:35:42,306 --> 00:35:43,266
He used my seal

554
00:35:43,346 --> 00:35:45,545
to forge a false testimony
and submitted it to the Emperor.

555
00:35:47,306 --> 00:35:48,386
If I overturn it,

556
00:35:49,025 --> 00:35:50,346
I would commit the crime of lying

557
00:35:51,185 --> 00:35:52,386
which would not only endanger me

558
00:35:53,025 --> 00:35:56,266
but the entire Shen family.

559
00:36:06,306 --> 00:36:08,145
Zishan, we all believe in you.

560
00:36:09,225 --> 00:36:11,266
There will absolutely be
no betrayal or suspicion among us.

561
00:36:13,065 --> 00:36:15,505
Let's talk about solutions.

562
00:36:16,665 --> 00:36:21,306
Chengfeng, if you have any
new investigative leads or instructions,

563
00:36:22,225 --> 00:36:23,386
just give them to me.

564
00:36:24,266 --> 00:36:25,466
I will do my best.

565
00:36:26,505 --> 00:36:29,145
It will also count as my way
of making amends to you.

566
00:36:39,868 --> 00:36:40,705
(Admiring High Mountains)

567
00:36:40,705 --> 00:36:42,346
Chengfeng, tell me.

568
00:36:43,145 --> 00:36:44,585
Since the minister is in the court,

569
00:36:45,266 --> 00:36:47,505
it's not difficult for you
to find out who impeached you.

570
00:36:48,625 --> 00:36:50,946
Why didn't you tell Danqing just now?

571
00:36:56,145 --> 00:36:57,266
I know you would never betray me.

572
00:36:57,906 --> 00:36:58,826
So, needless to say that.

573
00:37:00,826 --> 00:37:03,225
