because of it, right?

575
00:37:06,786 --> 00:37:09,025
Is that how you think of me?

576
00:37:09,466 --> 00:37:10,786
I was discontented with you before.

577
00:37:12,025 --> 00:37:12,585
And I hit you.

578
00:37:14,426 --> 00:37:16,306
It's only human for you to doubt me.

579
00:37:16,786 --> 00:37:17,545
That's not related.

580
00:37:18,986 --> 00:37:19,906
I've said it before.

581
00:37:20,505 --> 00:37:22,426
Even after the fight,
we're still brothers.

582
00:37:24,025 --> 00:37:24,986
I'm fair and clear.

583
00:37:25,986 --> 00:37:26,625
You've saved me

584
00:37:26,946 --> 00:37:27,585
and bound me.

585
00:37:28,105 --> 00:37:28,826
So we're even now.

586
00:37:29,866 --> 00:37:32,346
I will give my all for the treasure map.

587
00:37:34,306 --> 00:37:37,185
Great, let's find the map
and the developing water

588
00:37:37,665 --> 00:37:38,386
as soon as possible.

589
00:37:39,025 --> 00:37:39,746
Yeah.

590
00:37:56,426 --> 00:37:58,266
If there's anything, just say it.

591
00:38:00,065 --> 00:38:01,426
I don't get it.

592
00:38:02,145 --> 00:38:03,946
You spoke so bluntly with Shen Zishan,

593
00:38:04,866 --> 00:38:06,346
