What about now?

613
00:39:19,306 --> 00:39:19,906
Still annoying.

614
00:39:20,266 --> 00:39:21,065
It will make me fat.

615
00:39:21,545 --> 00:39:23,426
A bit of chubbiness is cute.

616
00:39:26,826 --> 00:39:29,306
I will accompany you
to the winery today.

617
