to find the problem.

634
00:40:25,866 --> 00:40:28,306
I see others tasting the wine.
Don't you try it?

635
00:40:29,866 --> 00:40:31,946
After checking the color and smell,
the next step is tasting.

636
00:40:32,426 --> 00:40:34,746
But I've found the issue by the smell,

637
00:40:34,986 --> 00:40:35,826
