638
00:40:36,266 --> 00:40:38,946
Shouldn't you taste it
to be absolutely sure?

639
00:40:40,986 --> 00:40:42,585
You're right, Ying'er.

640
00:40:49,746 --> 00:40:50,625
(You can observe her.)

641
00:40:51,585 --> 00:40:53,665
(She has a habit when she tastes wine.)

642
00:41:02,826 --> 00:41:04,585
It's undoubtedly an issue
with the flower juice.

643
00:41:08,225 --> 00:41:09,986
What's wrong, Ying'er?

644
00:41:11,306 --> 00:41:14,025
No, I'm just impressed.

645
00:41:14,306 --> 00:41:16,306
I never knew you were
so good at winemaking.

646
