Ying'er, I...

650
00:41:26,386 --> 00:41:26,986
Don't worry.

651
00:41:27,185 --> 00:41:29,306
When you have time, bring me
to see the winemaking process.

652
00:41:29,826 --> 00:41:30,585
I'll stay back

653
